   http://pkg-mono.alioth.debian.org/cli-policy/index.html


   MONO PATH setting
   export MONO_PATH=`pwd`
   export MONO_PATH="`pwd`:/usr/lib/nunit"
   export PATH="$PATH:$MONO_PATH"
  
   This hack of appennding the MONO_PATH to the PATH is unfortunately needed
   for NANT to work.
 
   See examples in mono.sh which can be invoked by 

   source mono.sh
